<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 20:06:50 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列承认真主党袭击对战略空军基地造成严重破坏</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-01-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-admits-hezbollah-strike-caused-extensive-damage-to-strategic-airbase/0000018c-e518-db55-a39e-f79ccc940000</link><description>真主党的导弹是向以色列北部的梅龙基地发射的。虽然铁穹系统可以拦截火箭弹，但以色列没有拦截真主党使用的反坦克导弹的系统</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 19:12:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-01-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-admits-hezbollah-strike-caused-extensive-damage-to-strategic-airbase/0000018c-e518-db55-a39e-f79ccc940000</guid></item><item><title>地区冲突迫在眉睫，美国国务卿布林肯抵达以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-01-07/ty-article/.premium/u-s-secretary-of-state-blinken-arriving-in-israel-as-regional-conflict-looms/0000018c-e4d7-d249-a1ce-efd78a0c0000</link><description>加沙的人道主义危机、黎巴嫩与真主党的边境紧张局势、哈马斯仍扣押的 130 多名人质——美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯周一访问以色列期间将有很多要讨论的内容</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 18:53:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-01-07/ty-article/.premium/u-s-secretary-of-state-blinken-arriving-in-israel-as-regional-conflict-looms/0000018c-e4d7-d249-a1ce-efd78a0c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列喜剧演员的加沙“旅行博客”视频引起社交媒体愤怒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-comedians-gaza-travel-blog-video-causes-social-media-outrage/0000018c-e4c5-db55-a39e-f7d585810000</link><description>喜剧演员盖伊·霍赫曼曾多次随以色列军队进入加沙地带，他在被毁坏的巴勒斯坦房屋和海滩上拍摄了一段嘲讽视频。以色列国防军表示，霍赫曼上次访问没有获得适当的授权，他们正在调查这一事件</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 18:22:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-comedians-gaza-travel-blog-video-causes-social-media-outrage/0000018c-e4c5-db55-a39e-f7d585810000</guid></item><item><title>分享一年前新闻的以色列 X 账户是对我们未来的持续警告信号</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-israeli-x-account-that-shares-news-from-a-year-ago-is-a-warning-sign-for-our-future/0000018c-e3fd-d614-a3cf-effdec5a0000</link><description>“一年前的新闻”开始发布去年的新闻，当时新冠疫情是以色列人能想象到的最可怕的事情。然后，10 月 7 日和加沙战争恰逢以色列极端主义政府成立的日子。到目前为止，该页面的关注者知道情况只会变得更糟</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 17:46:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-israeli-x-account-that-shares-news-from-a-year-ago-is-a-warning-sign-for-our-future/0000018c-e3fd-d614-a3cf-effdec5a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列任命前最高法院院长阿哈伦·巴拉克为国际法院种族灭绝案司法小组成员</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-appoints-ex-top-court-president-aharon-barak-to-judge-panel-in-icj-hearing/0000018c-e4f0-db55-a39e-f7f4a4a60000</link><description>巴拉克在该案中的任命，涉及南非对以色列在加沙行动的投诉，是基于以色列作为案件当事方，除了国际法院常规的 15 名法官组成的小组之外，还有权任命一名法官</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 17:27:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-appoints-ex-top-court-president-aharon-barak-to-judge-panel-in-icj-hearing/0000018c-e4f0-db55-a39e-f7f4a4a60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列大学寻求对分享减少 10 月 7 日大屠杀帖子的学生进行更严厉的惩罚</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-07/ty-article/.premium/university-seeks-stiffer-punishment-of-student-who-shared-post-diminishing-oct-7-massacre/0000018c-e47d-db55-a39e-f7fdb8c10000</link><description>大学纪律委员会决定对她进行谴责并责令她从事社区服务，引发了校园抗议。该大学校长建议该学生“明天不要像什么事都没发生一样返回学校”，而是“在图书馆或任何你认为合适的地方”学习</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 17:00:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-07/ty-article/.premium/university-seeks-stiffer-punishment-of-student-who-shared-post-diminishing-oct-7-massacre/0000018c-e47d-db55-a39e-f7fdb8c10000</guid></item><item><title>摩托车司机因用头盔殴打驾车者被判入狱30个月</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-07/ty-article/.premium/motorcycle-driver-sentenced-to-30-months-in-prison-for-hitting-motorist-with-helmet/0000018c-e457-dc46-a1ec-feffc61b0000</link><description>根据起诉书，重罪犯“没有停止攻击”受害者，“即使受害者倒在地上”，并且“立即用头盔击打他，直到受害者倒在路上并失去知觉才停止”</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 15:40:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-07/ty-article/.premium/motorcycle-driver-sentenced-to-30-months-in-prison-for-hitting-motorist-with-helmet/0000018c-e457-dc46-a1ec-feffc61b0000</guid></item><item><title>两名加沙记者在以色列空袭中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-07/ty-article/two-gaza-journalists-killed-in-apparent-israeli-airstrike/0000018c-e41e-d614-a3cf-ec9f7a880000</link><description>据哈马斯政府媒体办公室称，哈姆扎·达杜赫和穆斯塔法·塔拉亚在拉法的汽车被袭击身亡</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 14:33:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-07/ty-article/two-gaza-journalists-killed-in-apparent-israeli-airstrike/0000018c-e41e-d614-a3cf-ec9f7a880000</guid></item><item><title>为什么以色列不能轰炸哈马斯让其屈服</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-01-07/ty-article-opinion/.premium/why-israel-cant-bomb-hamas-into-submission/0000018c-e3ea-d614-a3cf-effb7b850000</link><description>2016年，内塔尼亚胡在议会会议厅读到一本书，书中主张通过压倒性的暴力才能赢得决定性的战争，这引起了轰动。但哈马斯和加沙的独特因素以及地区局势升级的威胁意味着以色列无法使用“投降或死亡”的最后通牒</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 13:53:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-01-07/ty-article-opinion/.premium/why-israel-cant-bomb-hamas-into-submission/0000018c-e3ea-d614-a3cf-effb7b850000</guid></item><item><title>以色列男子在约旦河西岸枪击事件中被枪杀，军队正在搜寻嫌疑人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-man-shot-dead-in-west-bank-shooting-attack-army-searches-for-suspects/0000018c-e3dc-d614-a3cf-efddb6190000</link><description>受害者名叫阿马尔·曼苏尔，32岁，东耶路撒冷居民</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 12:52:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-man-shot-dead-in-west-bank-shooting-attack-army-searches-for-suspects/0000018c-e3dc-d614-a3cf-efddb6190000</guid></item><item><title>以色列边境女警察被杰宁炸弹炸死；七名巴勒斯坦人在以色列国防军空袭中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-07/ty-article/israeli-border-policewoman-killed-by-jenin-bomb-seven-palestinians-killed-in-idf-air-raid/0000018c-e373-de22-abbe-e37ba6110000</link><description>杰宁的消息来源称，在无人机袭击中丧生的人手无寸铁，坐在路边的人行道上，其中四人是兄弟。以色列官员称，飞机向袭击该市军队的巴勒斯坦武装分子开火</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 11:58:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-07/ty-article/israeli-border-policewoman-killed-by-jenin-bomb-seven-palestinians-killed-in-idf-air-raid/0000018c-e373-de22-abbe-e37ba6110000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总理本-格维尔：“自愿”转移加沙人是解决方案，以色列人应该重新安置加沙地带</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-07/ty-article/ben-gvir-voluntary-transfer-of-gazans-is-the-solution-israelis-should-re-settle-strip/0000018c-e2f0-d751-ad8d-fff4fb4d0000</link><description>以色列极右翼部长声称这一想法得到了共和党候选人尼基·黑利的支持，并表示他将“努力说服”其他政府成员支持这一措施。几天前，国际法院将听取南非请愿书，指控以色列是强迫加沙人流离失所的幕后黑手</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 10:28:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-07/ty-article/ben-gvir-voluntary-transfer-of-gazans-is-the-solution-israelis-should-re-settle-strip/0000018c-e2f0-d751-ad8d-fff4fb4d0000</guid></item><item><title>真主党主席期待与以色列达成边境协议，但战争有其自身的规则</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-07/ty-article/.premium/nasrallah-sees-opportunity-for-an-israeli-border-deal-but-warfare-has-its-own-rules/0000018c-e346-d213-a1ed-ff5f15850000</link><description>纳斯鲁拉兑现了为贝鲁特一名哈马斯高级官员被暗杀的誓言，但仍谨慎行事 ■ 真主党愿意划定黎巴嫩与以色列的边界，可能会扩大该国与以色列的外交渠道，但障碍仍然存在</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 10:06:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-07/ty-article/.premium/nasrallah-sees-opportunity-for-an-israeli-border-deal-but-warfare-has-its-own-rules/0000018c-e346-d213-a1ed-ff5f15850000</guid></item><item><title>真主党对哈马斯领导人被杀事件的“遏制”反应后，以色列寻求避免北部敌对行动升级</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-07/ty-article/.premium/hezbollah-response-to-arouri-death-appears-contained-crossfire-could-go-on-for-months/0000018c-e096-ddba-abad-e2b7a3f00000</link><description>目前，真主党似乎对升级冲突不感兴趣，尽管离开北部家园的以色列人可能会等待数月才返回 ■ 内塔尼亚胡继续反对以色列国防军领导人 ■ 以色列军队接近哈马斯高级人物，但人质可能会受到束缚它们之间</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 04:01:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-07/ty-article/.premium/hezbollah-response-to-arouri-death-appears-contained-crossfire-could-go-on-for-months/0000018c-e096-ddba-abad-e2b7a3f00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队称其对黎巴嫩的袭击正在击退真主党的精锐部队</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-07/ty-article-live/blinken-israel-lebanon-border-is-area-of-real-concern/0000018c-e1d5-ddba-abad-e3f5e9be0000</link><description>以色列国防军证实真主党在周六的袭击中袭击了战略空军基地 ■ 以色列国防军主席称战争将持续全年 ■ 布林肯猛烈抨击本格维尔和斯莫特里奇关于加沙人口转移的言论 ■ 以色列称哈马斯在加沙北部的军事框架被拆除 ■ 超过 1,300 名平民和自 10 月 7 日以来，以色列士兵被杀；超过 136 名人质仍被扣押在加沙 ■ 哈马斯卫生部声称自 10 月 7 日以来已有 22,835 名巴勒斯坦人死亡，58,416 人受伤</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 03:43:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-07/ty-article-live/blinken-israel-lebanon-border-is-area-of-real-concern/0000018c-e1d5-ddba-abad-e3f5e9be0000</guid></item><item><title>获释的以色列人质在集会上作证：“我们遇到了遭受性虐待的人质”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-07/ty-article/.premium/freed-israeli-hostages-testify-at-rally-we-met-hostages-who-were-sexually-abused/0000018c-e0d0-ddba-abad-e2f10bed0000</link><description>特拉维夫集会上放映了从哈马斯囚禁中返回的获释以色列人质的证词，以支持仍被关押在加沙的人质家人。罗米·科恩（Romi Cohen）的双胞胎兄弟被绑架：“我担心人们开始忘记他们。不要离开我们。时间不多了&amp;#39;</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jan 2024 23:01:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-07/ty-article/.premium/freed-israeli-hostages-testify-at-rally-we-met-hostages-who-were-sexually-abused/0000018c-e0d0-ddba-abad-e2f10bed0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列大学撤销了八名学生的停学决定，该校声称在社交媒体上支持哈马斯</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-06/ty-article/.premium/university-reverses-suspension-of-8-students-it-claims-supported-hamas-on-social-media/0000018c-e080-daf6-a5df-e7fcbaff0000</link><description>在以色列阿拉伯少数民族权利法律中心阿达拉提出上诉后，纪律官员决定撤销暂停资格。海法大学试图让这些学生停课，声称他们的存在可能会导致“极端情况”</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jan 2024 21:01:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-06/ty-article/.premium/university-reverses-suspension-of-8-students-it-claims-supported-hamas-on-social-media/0000018c-e080-daf6-a5df-e7fcbaff0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军公布周六在加沙地带北部战斗中丧生的以色列士兵姓名</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-06/ty-article/.premium/idf-releases-name-of-israeli-soldier-killed-in-combat-in-the-northern-gaza-strip/0000018c-e03d-daf6-a5df-e77d6f470000</link><description>31 岁的 Roee Yohay Yosef Mordechay 留下了他的妻子 Neta 和他们的小女儿 Ori，Ori 出生于犹太新年</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jan 2024 20:05:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-06/ty-article/.premium/idf-releases-name-of-israeli-soldier-killed-in-combat-in-the-northern-gaza-strip/0000018c-e03d-daf6-a5df-e77d6f470000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡联盟上任一年后公布司法候选人名单</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-06/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-coalition-publishes-list-of-judicial-candidates-a-year-after-taking-office/0000018c-e032-ddba-abad-e2b3136c0000</link><description>司法任命委员会将于二月和三月审查以色列各地法院的数十名未来法官</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jan 2024 19:52:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-06/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-coalition-publishes-list-of-judicial-candidates-a-year-after-taking-office/0000018c-e032-ddba-abad-e2b3136c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列各地数千人抗议，要求举行选举并罢免内塔尼亚胡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-06/ty-article/.premium/thousands-protest-across-israel-calling-for-elections-and-netanyahus-dismissal/0000018c-dfc8-d751-ad8d-ffec1dc00000</link><description>“政府不仅把一箱箱钱交给哈马斯，还一路卖给我们，加沙边境社区的居民。它放弃了我们，他们的谎言于 10 月 7 日在我们面前爆炸了。”加利·巴苏多 (Gali Basudo) 在特拉维夫集会上说道</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jan 2024 19:04:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-06/ty-article/.premium/thousands-protest-across-israel-calling-for-elections-and-netanyahus-dismissal/0000018c-dfc8-d751-ad8d-ffec1dc00000</guid></item></channel></rss>